Morton, Timothy Dartmouth Stellar Evolution Grids <p>Dartmouth stellar model grids, used by the 'isochrones' python package (github.com/timothydmorton/isochrones).  Update from previous grids; these now include WISE bands, ages < 1Gyr, and have coarser Fe/H sampling.</p> 2015-03-04
    https://zenodo.org/record/15843/files/dartmouth.tri; https://zenodo.org/record/15843/files/dartmouth.h5;
